      <title>纽约市长迅速撤销贿赂指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/nyc-mayor-adams-moves-quickly-to-dismiss-bribery-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 迅速采取行动，为自己辩护以对抗联邦腐败指控，周一他请求法官驳回一项“根本不构成联邦罪行”的贿赂指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/nyc-mayor-adams-moves-quickly-to-dismiss-bribery-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:32:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国保守党在平静的工作日后直面反对派的现实</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/uk-conservative-party-faces-up-to-opposition-reality-after-quiet-business-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国保守党在今年的年度大会上很难完成企业日活动，这与该党作为英国商界政党的自我品牌形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/uk-conservative-party-faces-up-to-opposition-reality-after-quiet-business-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:06:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚侨民债券或将为备受争议的机场升级项目提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/kenya-diaspora-bond-may-help-fund-controversial-airport-upgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总理内阁秘书穆萨利亚·穆达瓦迪表示，肯尼亚计划发行的侨民债券可能用于资助关键基础设施项目，包括该国最繁忙机场的扩建计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/kenya-diaspora-bond-may-help-fund-controversial-airport-upgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:50:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国向中东增派数千名士兵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/us-deploys-a-few-thousand-more-troops-to-middle-east</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼称，随着以色列加大对黎巴嫩真主党的攻击力度，美国将向中东增派数千名士兵以保卫以色列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/us-deploys-a-few-thousand-more-troops-to-middle-east</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>危地马拉总统称“腐败联盟”计划卷土重来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/guatemala-s-president-says-corrupt-coalition-plans-a-comeback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[危地马拉总统贝尔纳多·阿雷瓦洛表示，那些几乎阻挠他今年就职典礼的政客和官员现在正试图破坏他打击腐败、增加基础设施和社会支出的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/guatemala-s-president-says-corrupt-coalition-plans-a-comeback</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:28:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国预计以色列将对黎巴嫩真主党进行有限袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/limited-israeli-incursion-into-lebanon-may-be-imminent-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名美国官员称，华盛顿警告以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡的政府不要采取更大规模和更长期的铲除真主党的行动后，美国预计以色列将对黎巴嫩南部发动有限的地面入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/limited-israeli-incursion-into-lebanon-may-be-imminent-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:10:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州严厉打击零售盗窃、毒​​品犯罪，赢得 70 多位市长支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/push-for-tougher-retail-and-drug-penalties-in-california-gains-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州一项旨在打击商店盗窃和毒品犯罪的投票措施正在投票表决中，该措施得到了大型零售商、执法团体、一位加密货币亿万富翁以及现在超过 70 位市长的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/push-for-tougher-retail-and-drug-penalties-in-california-gains-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨称德国经济需要更多移民来促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/scholz-says-german-economy-needs-more-migrants-to-boost-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨表示，德国必须吸引更多来自国外的技术工人，并加快将新移民融入劳动力市场，以帮助陷入困境的经济重回正轨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/scholz-says-german-economy-needs-more-migrants-to-boost-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:59:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯发表灾难性言论 希拉里·海伦扰乱竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/helene-disrupts-race-as-trump-harris-move-to-address-disaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风海伦正在震撼总统竞选，在关键的摇摆州留下一条满目疮痍的痕迹，并迫使唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯的竞争对手竞选团队转向应对灾难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/helene-disrupts-race-as-trump-harris-move-to-address-disaster</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:34:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯和沃尔兹将在势均力敌的选举中进行最后辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/vance-walz-set-to-spar-in-final-debate-of-tight-election-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[选举日还有五周时间，JD Vance 和 Tim Walz 将举行一场副总统辩论，以期在共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普和民主党对手卡马拉·哈里斯之间做出选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/vance-walz-set-to-spar-in-final-debate-of-tight-election-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
